01:09:55.230 --> 01:10:01.170
And that study was really paned by everything.

01:10:01.170 --> 01:10:02.940
Because they said give us a cost analysis.

01:10:02.940 --> 01:10:07.310
And I really thought they wanted to know what
it was going to cost so I told them.

01:10:07.310 --> 01:10:10.420
Well, they didn't like it.

01:10:10.420 --> 01:10:16.060
And, in all honesty, I really wasn't that
